SELECT LINE_ID FROM MSTM_EMS_CONNECTIVITY_LINE WHERE AUTH_STAT ='A' AND RECORD_STAT ='O' AND UPPER( OPERATION_MODE)='OUTBOUND' AND CONNECTION_TYPE=?
SELECT * FROM MSTM_EMS_OVERLAP_PROTOCOL WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND PROTOCOL=?
select RULE_GRP_NAME from MSTM_EMS_RULE_GROUP WHERE RECORD_STAT='O' AND AUTH_STAT='A'
SELECT BULK_RULE_NAME from MSTM_EMS_BULK_RULE WHERE RECORD_STAT='O' AND AUTH_STAT='A'
